# Bank of lexical games (FCE Unit 3 — *My digital detox*)

**Page:** `unit3-digital-detox/lexical-games-digital-detox.html` — tab on `unit3-digital-detox/index.html` and `exam-mode-reading-p5.html`.

**Scope:** **FCE Unit 3 only.** All phrase data and game pages live under `unit3-digital-detox/` (`data/u3-digital-detox-lexis.js`, `games/`, `word-bank-digital-detox.html`, etc.).

**Do not** add *My digital detox* as a theme, Word Bank pack, fall pool, or typed-gap pack in the main site `index.html` (CPE / Level 9 / `cpeWordBank`). The user may reuse *ideas* from those UIs (labels like Word bank, Pair blitz), but implementation stays in the Unit 3 folder.

**Optional asset:** `unit3-digital-detox/data/u3-digital-detox-passage-plain.js` — full article plain text for future on-disk mechanics; regenerate with `node scripts/extract-u3-digital-detox-plain.mjs`.

## When editing

- Keep links relative to `unit3-digital-detox/`.
- If the seven labels are remapped, update this file and `lexical-games-digital-detox.html` together.
